                SF_Reset
            

        




Help version 2.0 / Issue date: 2024.03
The following description is valid for the function block SF_Reset_V1_0z, Version 1.0z (where z = 0 to 9).




	
										Short Description
										The SF_Reset function block provides a manual reset function. The reset signal at the ResetOut output takes place as a short TRUE pulse with a length of one cycle of the Safety PLC, if a manual reset is requested at the ResetIn input....
